<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>accurate in something • accurate with something</xh5><p> <i>accurate in something—</i>free from mistakes in what one says or does: He was basically careful and <u>accurate in</u> his quotations and references to sources.</p><p> <i>accurate with something—</i>careful about smth.; treating smth. with responsibility: When writing a composition, be <u>accurate with</u> your quotations.</p></entry>
